/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"f913d29db2bde5c9c46b813d0f54be03599e7ad0","tid":1650630,"uid":200389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2cbae6e743b6f3ed64335f98dfd8769a226243d","tid":1650630,"uid":143119,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:06:13.000Z","msg":"jupas個陣9揀諗住揀vet點知揀錯左vet nurse<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要accept左offer"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:01:13.000Z","msg":"Ching rejupas啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217302c4631634dd5593920b5ae66ecb0a1563b4","tid":1650630,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3281cd07c7547c635b49c14c05065c31944286a7","tid":1650630,"uid":272840,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T07:45:11.000Z","msg":"係呢啲時間仲講收生分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:03:26.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n應該allin抗爭由班港豬讀大學<br />\n反正條條大路通羅馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a29dede77dfeef1ac796484e9e80a05ba9bd53","tid":1650630,"uid":275058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:09:46.000Z","msg":"Best 25分 讀llb <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52583dfd6705a5f1d238ea0e97b98e4a304ed573","tid":1650630,"uid":143119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f913d29db2bde5c9c46b813d0f54be03599e7ad0","tid":1650630,"uid":200389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2cbae6e743b6f3ed64335f98dfd8769a226243d","tid":1650630,"uid":143119,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:06:13.000Z","msg":"jupas個陣9揀諗住揀vet點知揀錯左vet nurse<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要accept左offer"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:01:13.000Z","msg":"Ching rejupas啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" cl